{"pin":"BH00272","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00272","anchor":"","first_line":"The purpose of the one true God, exalted be His glory, in revealing Himself unto men is to lay bare those gems that lie hidden within the mine of their true and inmost selves… So powerful is the light of unity","first_line_orig":"حق جل جلاله از برای ظهور جواهر معانی از معدن انسانی آمده الیوم دین الله و مذهب  ","language":"5","word_count":"2340","subjects":"@oneness; unity of religion, @consorting with all; being kind; loving to all, @rejection, opposition and persecution, @suffering and imprisonment, @service to others; to the Cause of God, @call to action, @unity; oneness of humanity, @steadfastness; perseverance; faithfulness, @love and unity, @honesty; truthfulness; trustworthiness","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#20\"\u003eLL#020\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleani